    "Table 2 presents the MARB, DSS and IS values obtained for the missing data in each model.",
    "We summarize the measures for three-years periods with varying percentages of available incidence data.",
    "This includes periods 2001-2003 (70% available), 2004-2006 (75% available), and so on, up to 2013-2015 (93% available) (see Figure 5 for details).",
    "Based on the MARB analysis, Model 3 performs the best for three-year periods with 70% or 75% data availability.",
    "When this percentage increases, all three models show similar MARB performance."
